data.description: Charming Full Brick Rancher on large corner lot. Large fenced in backyard with screened in rear porch and 110x15 storage building. The living room boasts vaulted ceilings with a raised hearth brick fireplace that steals the show. Beautiful tile floors and shiplap feature walls. New paint in LR and Dining area as well as LR ceilings.  Master bedroom bath has new walk in shower installed in 2023.  All three bedrooms have new carpet. Kitchen has large sink, and tile flooring. New stainless dishwasher in 2023.  Fridge, and range in 2022. Hot Water Heater in 2018.
